<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,847,1028]" box="[151,839,886,912]" pageId="11" pageNumber="60">
Basionym:— 
<taxonomicName authority="Wang (1984 b: 21)" authorityName="Wang" authorityPageNumber="21" authorityYear="1984" box="[307,835,886,912]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Didymocarpus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="11" pageNumber="60" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="mollifolius">
<emphasis box="[307,612,887,912]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="60">Didymocarpus mollifolius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Wang, W. T." box="[620,835,886,912]" pageId="11" pageNumber="60" pagination="11 - 26" refId="ref9643" refString="Wang, W. T. (1984 b) Notulae de Gesneriaceis Sinensibus (VI). Acta Botanica Yunnanica 6 (1): 11 - 26." type="journal article" year="1984">Wang (1984b: 21)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="11.[151,1436,847,1028]" pageId="11" pageNumber="60">
Notes:—No molecular data available, but the species is similar to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Hemsley" authorityYear="1890" box="[950,1059,925,950]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Didymocarpus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="11" pageNumber="60" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hancei">
<emphasis box="[950,1059,925,950]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="60">P. hancei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<emphasis box="[1120,1314,925,950]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="60">
<taxonomicName authorityName="D. Fang &amp; W. T. Wang" authorityYear="1982" box="[1120,1310,925,950]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Didymocarpus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="11" pageNumber="60" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="niveolanosus">P. niveolanosus</taxonomicName>
.
</emphasis>
The three species form a group of rosette plants (very unlike true 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Wallich" authorityYear="1819" box="[838,1016,964,989]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Gesneriaceae" genus="Didymocarpus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="11" pageNumber="60" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[838,1016,964,989]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="60">Didymocarpus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, for the morphology of which see 
<bibRefCitation author="Weber, A. &amp; Burtt, B. L." box="[151,392,1002,1028]" pageId="11" pageNumber="60" pagination="293 - 363" refId="ref10075" refString="Weber, A. &amp; Burtt, B. L. (1998, [&quot; 1997 &quot;]) Remodelling of Didymocarpus and associated genera (Gesneriaceae). Beitrage zur Biologie der Pflanzen 70 (2 - 3): 293 - 363." type="journal article" year="1998">Weber &amp; Burtt 1998</bibRefCitation>
) with oblong or oblanceolate leaves with pinnate venation.
</paragraph>
